    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_8_1768-1778",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1768-1778",
      "markText": "其谋臣皆不尽其忠也。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1768&rangeEnd=1778",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1768&rangeEnd=1778"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_22_1043-1075",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "1043-1075",
      "markText": "国小而不处卑，力少而不畏强，无礼而侮大邻，贪愎而拙交者，可亡也。",
      "totalCount": 44,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1043&rangeEnd=1075",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1043&rangeEnd=1075"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_2_626-662",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "626-662",
      "markText": "后来韩非应秦国之邀出使秦国，但未及被秦王政任用，便为李斯、姚贾谗言害死。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=626&rangeEnd=662",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=626&rangeEnd=662"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_17_1246-1289",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "1246-1289",
      "markText": "故竖穀阳之进酒，不以仇子反也，其心忠爱之，而适足以杀之。故曰：“行小忠，则大忠之贼也。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1289",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1289"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_56_842-863",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "842-863",
      "markText": "今欲以先王之政，治当世之民，皆守株之类也。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=842&rangeEnd=863",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=842&rangeEnd=863"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_3_675-736",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "675-736",
      "markText": "非论说固有偏激，然其云明法严刑，救群生之乱，去天下之祸，使强不陵弱，众不暴寡，耆老得遂，幼孤得长，此则重典之用而张弛之宜，",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=675&rangeEnd=736",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=675&rangeEnd=736"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_2_1214-1227",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1214-1227",
      "markText": "抱法处势则治，背法去势则乱",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1214&rangeEnd=1227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1214&rangeEnd=1227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_2_1279-1365",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1279-1365",
      "markText": "韩非的法治思想不仅顺应了当时社会从群雄割据转向大一统君主集权制发展的需要，而且也对我国整个封建社会的发展产生了深远的影响，因此，《韩非子》是研究我国古代思想文化的重要资料。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1279&rangeEnd=1365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1279&rangeEnd=1365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_13_1121-1174",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1121-1174",
      "markText": "今若以誉进能，则臣离上而下比周；［20］若以党举官，则民务交而不求用于法。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1121&rangeEnd=1174",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1121&rangeEnd=1174"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_13_1736-1764",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1736-1764",
      "markText": "故明主使法择人，不自举也；使法量功，不自度也。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793496&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1736&rangeEnd=1764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b3281071c69cd827b259b?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1736&rangeEnd=1764"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793496_14_2738-2808",
